# CLIs — citty only

Applies to all CLI tools under **`apps/`**.

## Required

Implement command-line interfaces with **[citty](https://github.com/unjs/citty)**:

- `defineCommand` for each command and nested subcommand
- `runMain` (or `createMain`) in `src/cli.ts`
- Lazy `subCommands` for deep or large command trees
- **`packages/<app>/commoncli.ts`** — `define<App>Command` merges tool-wide
  flags on every node (citty does not inherit parent args)

Full patterns: [docs/agents/cli.md](../../docs/agents/cli.md).

## Forbidden

- Hand-rolled `process.argv` parsing for user-facing commands
- Other CLI frameworks: `commander`, `yargs`, `clipanion`, `cac`,
  `sade`, `meow`, `@effect/cli`

Subprocesses inside `run` handlers still use **`Bun.spawn`** per
[bun-spawn-subprocess.mdc](./bun-spawn-subprocess.mdc) — prefer placing
spawn calls in **`packages/<app>/main.ts`** per
[cli-command-structure.mdc](./cli-command-structure.mdc).
